  "prompt": "Is there any Indian on Quora who did MS,MBA in USA but did not get a job after completion of course and had to return to India?",
  "response": "Yes, there are individuals on platforms like Quora who have shared their experiences of pursuing higher education, such as an MS or MBA, in the United States but then facing challenges in securing a job there after graduation. Several factors can influence such outcomes, including the job market conditions, visa-related issues, personal circumstances, or mismatches between the candidate's skills and employers' requirements.\n\nIf you're looking for specific stories or discussions, you can search directly on Quora using keywords related to this topic. You'll likely find first-hand accounts and advice from those who have been in similar situations. Keep in mind that individual experiences can vary widely and what might be true for one person may not be the same for another.",
